### DTDE Region Sharding API Tests
### This file tests property-based sharding by region (EU, US, APAC)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ============================================
### CUSTOMERS - Sharded by Region
### ============================================

### Create EU Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hans Mueller",
  "email": "hans@example.de",
  "region": "EU",
  "phone": "+49 123 456789",
  "address": "Berlin, Germany"
}

###

### Create US Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "region": "US",
  "phone": "+1 555 123 4567",
  "address": "New York, USA"
}

###

### Create APAC Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tanaka Yuki",
  "email": "tanaka@example.jp",
  "region": "APAC",
  "phone": "+81 3 1234 5678",
  "address": "Tokyo, Japan"
}

###

### Get all customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers

###

### Get customers by region (EU)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers?region=EU

###

### Get customers by region (US)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers?region=US

###

### Get customer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1

###

### ============================================
### ORDERS - Sharded by Region (co-located)
### ============================================

### Create order for EU customer (customer 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "shippingAddress": "Berlin, Germany",
  "items": [
    {
      "productSku": "LAPTOP-001",
      "productName": "Gaming Laptop",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 1299.99
    },
    {
      "productSku": "MOUSE-001",
      "productName": "Wireless Mouse",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 49.99
    }
  ]
}

###

### Create order for US customer (customer 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 2,
  "shippingAddress": "New York, USA",
  "items": [
    {
      "productSku": "PHONE-001",
      "productName": "Smartphone Pro",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 999.99
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get orders by region (EU)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/region/EU

###

### Get orders for customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/customer/1

###

### Get order statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/stats

###

### Get orders by region (US)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/region/US

###
